race.comment: RIVERSDALE MICK (1) was a (29.59) winner last time out at Sandown from Box 4. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Expected to be right there at the finish again. ALL JAZZ (4) missed the frame latest when eighth at Bendigo (28.68) but scored five back at The Meadows (29.98). Has never been out of the money in three starts this course and distance. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to her credit. Key runner on best form. FURIOUS FALCON (2) boasts a strong record this course with five wins and four minors from 14 tries. Was out of placings last time (30.13) at Sandown in a Grade 5, finishing fifth and beaten 7 lengths. Suited here and expected to run well. BETTY'S GARDEN (3) ran good time (25.85) when second last start over 460m at Warragul, the second placing in a row.
